name: Lay Bankz
description: '''Layia Watkins''' (born June 11, 2004), known professionally as '''Lay Bankz''', is an American singer and rapper. After signing a record contract with [[Artist Partner Group]] (APG) in 2022, she released the singles "Left Cheek (Doo Doo Blick)", "Na Na Na" and "Ick" the following year. Her 2024 single, "[[Tell Ur Girlfriend]]" became popular on [[TikTok]] and marked her first entry on the [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]].
